{"tid":764194,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一個人努力做嘢，開始唔知為咗啲咩。","createTime":"2018-08-01T17:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T01:10:42.000Z","uid":110381,"like":57,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"5d2285f37a4f4f3776b0d0b8bd26fc775f5aaf6e","tid":764194,"uid":110381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T17:52:22.000Z","msg":"分手之後，一直好努力做嘢<br />\n初初覺得呢個方法唔錯，可以唔洗諗咁多嘢<br />\n但依家有時返到屋企，好攰好攰，攰到想一睡不醒嘅時候⋯⋯⋯ 就開始諗，自己咁搏命，其實為咗啲咩？<br />\n就算俾我將來做到有成績又點？<br />\n我已經係對生活厭倦，對感情疲態，一條行屍走肉嘅臭蟲。<br />\n<br />\n純放負，完。"},{"pid":"28e7388ee3bb8b96e7704a16bf161a3885669c26","tid":764194,"uid":78264,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T17:55:42.000Z","msg":"真係唔知為乜撚"},{"pid":"7938fd0a1490dee59db94535ccd9c22bbabcb30c","tid":764194,"uid":110381,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"28e7388ee3bb8b96e7704a16bf161a3885669c26","tid":764194,"uid":78264,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T17:55:42.000Z","msg":"真係唔知為乜撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T17:58:51.000Z","msg":"如果屋企唔係等你養，你就真係毫無價值架喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5832de9e5246094a205fdb8b201acc4a1f7794e0","tid":764194,"uid":161537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T18:23:30.000Z","msg":"等機會來到"},{"pid":"d5e750cf402078fd2ebec31c12ca690db0e067c7","tid":764194,"uid":144788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T19:15:32.000Z","msg":"岩岩分手，都係有你呢個諗法，聽日唔想返工了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"758f3e883ccf4ed7c5f351e0354d0cc3f2a9ff2f","tid":764194,"uid":110381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5832de9e5246094a205fdb8b201acc4a1f7794e0","tid":764194,"uid":161537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T18:23:30.000Z","msg":"等機會來到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T01:55:09.000Z","msg":"咩機會"},{"pid":"20d1fc2c9a20032873bdc1b69e02c4ff0e0c05b3","tid":764194,